name: Regular Fit Sports Windbreaker
description: Conscious choice New Arrival Regular-fit, lightweight sports jacket in windproof, functional fabric for comfort and protection from wind. Hood with elasticized edge.

name: Relaxed Fit Cotton T-shirt
description: Relaxed-fit T-shirt in soft cotton jersey with a printed design at front. Ribbed crew neck and dropped shoulders.

description: Slim-fit polo shirt in soft, fine-knit cotton. Collar, small V-shaped opening at top, and long sleeves. Fine ribbing at cuffs and hem.

description: Shirt in oxford cotton. Button-down collar, buttons without placket, and yoke at back. Open chest pocket, long sleeves with button at cuffs, and sleeve placket with link button.

name: Bomber Jacket
description: Bomber jacket with a ribbed stand-up collar and zipper at front.

name: Regular Jeans
description: 5-pocket jeans in stretch cotton denim. Regular waist, zip fly with button, and straight legs with good room for movement over thighs and knees.

name: Regular Jeans
description: 5-pocket jeans in stretch cotton denim. Regular waist, zip fly with button, and straight legs with good room for movement over thighs and knees.

name: Regular Fit Double-layered Sports Shorts
description: Regular-fit shorts in fast-drying, patterned mesh to help keep you dry and cool while exercising. Elasticized waistband with concealed drawstring, a back pocket with zipper, and a towel loop at back.

name: Slim Fit Pants
description: Slim-fit pants in twill. Waistband with concealed hook-and-eye fastener and a zip fly. Side pockets and welt back pockets with button.

name: Corduroy Bucket Hat
description: Conscious choice New Arrival Bucket hat in cotton corduroy. Embroidered eyelets at each side and sweatband in woven cotton fabric.
